{"tid":1550782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"被警犬插竹嫁禍手足有野想講","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T03:57:48.000Z","uid":184320,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b09f5672df49caebf076ee77424bf40e56007f3d","tid":1550782,"uid":184320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:38:15.000Z","msg":"我係嗰位手足既朋友 由於佢本人冇連登ac 所以代佢開個po<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9FAT2ne.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9FAT2ne.png&h=33c6ba91&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oGkkHne.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoGkkHne.jpg&h=e4fb7233&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0d78f03d91f383c5acac3d956ff206186075c08","tid":1550782,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:38:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58585f7c159a96dd762aa40296b99a38e826299c","tid":1550782,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油"},{"pid":"315e44b7a758a2cbcf529554dc805a83a390d859","tid":1550782,"uid":266805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:39:41.000Z","msg":"加油<br />\n冇事就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"366441697242e7d84dde19536b27744ed3ac000a","tid":1550782,"uid":69742,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce7f42f8eeb5a6a78024a7b39258850f0359479","tid":1550782,"uid":47905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:41:07.000Z","msg":"希望大家記得<br />\n比人捉左 就算你無罪 你都出唔到黎幫手<br />\n所以一定係要不被捕為原則<br />\n先可以每次都出到黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果想KEEP住每次活動都出一分力<br />\n拒絕留守 拒絕戀戰<br />\n行動完成就閃 撚完狗就閃 唔好明知對面增緊援,準備圍都仲唔散"},{"pid":"64500e6469c8ee109c4b9df38b73f4c65efa5adf","tid":1550782,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:42:21.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33cec8485bb4b68140998098f883d0b002ebcb2d","tid":1550782,"uid":270286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:42:35.000Z","msg":"咩誤會？<br />\nBTW 手足 好好休息下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05b638599c68ebdc58cc5c54c8af96f8a068308","tid":1550782,"uid":196697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b09f5672df49caebf076ee77424bf40e56007f3d","tid":1550782,"uid":184320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:38:15.000Z","msg":"我係嗰位手足既朋友 由於佢本人冇連登ac 所以代佢開個po<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9FAT2ne.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9FAT2ne.png&h=33c6ba91&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oGkkHne.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoGkkHne.jpg&h=e